Flash Message Conductor
============

A collection of helpers that we tend to use across most of our projects.


Example
=======

# Controller helpers

add_message( 'foo' )

is the equivalent of

flash[:message] = 'foo'

Controller helpers included:

add_message( message ) 
add_notice( message )
add_error( message )

# View helpers

<%= render_flash_messages %>

produces:

<div id="flash_messages">
  <p class="message">You have successfully done XYZ...</p>
</div>

# or... if you set an error

<div id="flash_messages">
  <p class="error">Oops! Something went bonkers!</p>
</div>



